result.name: Café de Coral

reviews.text: Have a nice seat. Eat something to have a good break. Recharge with good price/performance food : p

Shop is a normal one of Cafe de Coral  branch. But it is special. It is a recharge centre for hungered and tired city workers. The workers don't have much time and much bucks to enjoy the lunch in the middle of the day. I see many workers in their white shirts or clothes dusty and sweaty. We are all living in this small city performing each roles rolling this city. Staffs are nicer than any other its brand shop.
Enjoyed our lunch time there! Great food and great place!
Local fast food experience. Hongkong style.
Good food and good prices, but like most fast-food restaurants, difficult to find a table to eat at, especially when traveling as a group.
